></i>\n                    <h3>Voice Assistant</h3>\n                    <p>Control all your devices with simple voice commands. Hands-free convenience.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-cogs\"></i>\n                    <h3>Personalized Automation</h3>\n                    <p>Create custom routines and scenes that fit your unique lifestyle.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" style=\"background-color: var(--background-color);\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Aura</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">Aura is dedicated to simplifying your life through intuitive and powerful smart home solutions. Our technology is designed to be user-friendly, reliable, and future-proof, making your home smarter and more responsive than ever before.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"cta\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to Transform Your Home?</h2>\n            <p>Discover the Aura difference and step into a smarter, more connected future.</p>\n            <button class=\"cta-button\" onclick=\"alert('Thank you for your interest! Visit our full website for more details.');\">Learn More</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Aura Smart Home. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Connect with us: <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll animation trigger\n        document.addEventListener('scroll', () => {\n            const sections = document.querySelectorAll('section, .cta');\n            sections.forEach(section => {\n                const rect = section.getBoundingClientRect();\n                if (rect.top < window.innerHeight * 0.8) {\n                    section.style.animationPlayState = 'running';\n                }\n            });\n        });\n\n        // Trigger animations on load if already in view\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const sections = document.querySelectorAll('section, .cta');\n            sections.forEach(section => {\n                const rect = section.getBoundingClientRect();\n                if (rect.top < window.innerHeight) {\n                    section.style.animationPlayState = 'running';\n                }\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}